##DESCRIPTION
## Calculate power absorbed using voltage and current
##ENDDESCRIPTION
## DBsubject(Electric circuits)
## Institution(Louisiana Tech University)
## Author(Paul Hummel)
## KEYWORDS('Circuit Basics','DC Power','Power')
## RESOURCES('DC_Power_03.png')

